Democratic presidential candidate former Vice President Joe Biden, accompanied by his wife Jill, speaks to members of the press at the National Constitution Center in Philadelphia, Tuesday, March 10, 2020.
(AP Photo/Matt Rourke)As I wrote yesterday, it’s obvious Joe Biden is fully relying on teleprompters to allow him to maintain any semblance of a coherent though.
In it, we see Joe Biden appearing with his wife on one of MSNBC’s morning shows.
He then attempts to share an anecdote that turns into something so foreign that you’d think he’s speaking a different language.
Keep in mind, this happened on Morning Joe, a show famous for questioning Trump’s mental health.